data.description: ***Seller offering $2,000 towards Buyer's Closing Costs***Welcome home to this spacious 2 story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath, well maintained home. Upon entry everyone will notice the lovely crown molding throughout, cozy gas fireplace, and wonderful open floor plan. Your cooking experience will be enhanced with the large island and tons of granite countertop space for food prep. The home is prewired for 5.1 surround sound and dual HDMI & Coax connections above the fireplace. A cute front and back porch allow great shaded areas to enjoy the outdoors. The backyard is completely enclosed with an 8 foot privacy fence. Bonus features such as tankless water heater, 2 car garage and more make this home a great option for your next move!
